            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A family in Tucson, Arizona is reeling after a thief swiped two classic cars from their property. One is an orange 1927 Ford Model T coupe, the other a 1929 Ford Model A truck. Just to make it even worse, the thief swiped a 2006 Dodge Ram 3500 dually pickup as well.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
